verses.lines:
Ndyambala engule yange mu ggulu;
Yange mu ggulu, yange mu ggulu;
Ndyambala engule yange mu ggulu;
Walibaawo (e)ssanyu, (e)ssanyu.

Ffe tuli ggye lya Mukama,
Ggye lya Mukama, ggye lya Mukama;
Ffe tuli ggye lya Mukama, tumukolere.

Yesu ayagala (a)baana, abaana bonna mu nsi;
Tayinza kubagobera bweru, yagaan(a) okubagoba,
Era tabeerabira; n'obwana obukafiiri obw'ewala.

Yesu ayagala (a)baana, abaana bonna mu nsi;
Abeeru n'abakyenvu, naffe abaddugavu;
Yesu ayagala (a)baana b'omunsi.

Nkumi na nkumi bafa, eyo mu ns(i) ezewala;
Tebamanyi na kwagala kwa Yesu, tusab(e) era tugabe;
Balyoke bategeere, ekitiibwa ekibalindiridde.

Ka tubuulire wonna, obulungi bwa Yesu;
Enjiri ebune mu nnimi zonna, tuyimb(e) era tusuute,
Omulokozi waffe; n'abantu bonna bamutendereze.

Mp(a) amafuta mu ttabaaza yange;
Mp(a) amafuta ge nkusaba;
Mp(a) amafuta mu ttabaaza yange,
Njakenga okutuusa enkya,

Tumaze okusoma, tuddayo ewaffe,
Mweraba, mweraba, mubeere besigwa;
Mweraba, mweraba, Katond(a) abakuume.
